{"tid":1433902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［大台］一直以來推動呢場運動嘅，係集體智慧同道德直覺","createTime":"2019-08-08T15:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T16:47:46.000Z","uid":42364,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1cd7d4281a43938ac661547adc8d0c5b8f5797","tid":1433902,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:20:02.000Z","msg":"一直以來推動呢場運動嘅<br />\n係一眾香港人嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">集體智慧</span>同心底嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">道德直覺</span><br />\n某啲人直唔願意相信今次運動冇大台<br />\n係因為佢地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一直睇低香港人同年青人</span><br />\n以為香港人年青人冇足夠智慧<br />\n仲有佢地以自己<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">淪喪左既道德觀</span><br />\n去套係香港人身上<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以我地做既野佢地自己解釋唔到</span><br />\n正如二維生物無法理解三維"},{"pid":"62bd0b686b58cf1c953694074cc97d4357a35a38","tid":1433902,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:28:44.000Z","msg":"大台論同外國勢力論<br />\n講出黎嗰啲人唔on9<br />\n佢地說話嘅對象仲on9<br />\n點解廢中廢老藍絲會信到十足<br />\n因為廢中廢老藍絲日常生活都一路覺得<br />\n「啲細路邊有咁叻呀」<br />\n成日覺得自己最叻<br />\n啲後生最笨實"},{"pid":"b5506e1db25c5b4dce8d94a9d1c00debc481926d","tid":1433902,"uid":42364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:00:34.000Z","msg":"二維生物無法理解三維"},{"pid":"a9b4d65f8971408d06592fea407601dfa88dcb43","tid":1433902,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a192e60f4c5bf2367787d1b5d146393bfac894ae","tid":1433902,"uid":271051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"單細胞藍絲無法理解"},{"pid":"dbfe090da7c52ff20f55160d06bf5c37c4756e2a","tid":1433902,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:47:46.000Z","msg":"夏蟲不可語冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}